text: Pierre Schmitz (16 May 1920 - 7 December 2004) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:People from Differdange
